    <item>
      <title>Hechler-Fayd'herbe 表示，预计市场将出现波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-05/expect-volatility-in-markets-hechler-fayd-herbe-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[隆巴德奥迪尔银行的 Nannette Hechler-Fayd&#39;herbe 表示，尽管制造业数据“非常疲软”，但她并不认为美国即将陷入衰退。她在彭博电视上表示，她预计“市场将出现很大波动”。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-05/expect-volatility-in-markets-hechler-fayd-herbe-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 08:40:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瓦拉维纳称预计石油需求增长将放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-05/expect-oil-demand-growth-to-moderate-valavina-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[惠誉评级的安吉丽娜·瓦拉维纳 (Angelina Valavina) 对石油市场形势发表评论，称供应增加和需求增长放缓导致布伦特原油价格持续跌破每桶 80 美元大关。瓦拉维纳告诉彭博电视台：“与之前的预测相比，我们预计今年的需求增长将放缓至每天 100 万桶以下。”（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-05/expect-oil-demand-growth-to-moderate-valavina-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 08:37:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>一艘天然气运输船伪造位置帮助俄罗斯避免制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/a-gas-carrier-faking-its-location-helps-russia-avoid-sanctions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一艘停靠在受制裁的俄罗斯天然气设施的液化天然气运输船没有已知的保险公司，由一家鲜为人知的印度公司管理，并假装在其他地方。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/a-gas-carrier-faking-its-location-helps-russia-avoid-sanctions</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 08:33:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>私募股权市场低迷导致投资者更加依赖股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/private-equity-drought-has-made-investors-more-reliant-on-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[私募股权回报率的下滑使得美国养老金和捐赠基金越来越多地依赖一种古老而熟悉的投资：股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/private-equity-drought-has-made-investors-more-reliant-on-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 08:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>软银集团股价创1998年上市以来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/softbank-group-shares-plunge-most-since-going-public-in-1998</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，日本股市暴跌导致软银集团公司市值蒸发 150 亿美元，创下自 1998 年创始人孙正义带领公司上市以来的最大单日跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/softbank-group-shares-plunge-most-since-going-public-in-1998</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 07:23:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Sidara 以风险上升为由终止 Wood Group 收购谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/sidara-ends-wood-group-takeover-talks-citing-rising-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[工程公司 Sidara 表示不会对 John Wood Group Plc 提出明确收购要约，结束了长达数月的求购过程。]]></description>
